#org @defeatText
= [.]\nAnd to a criminal..!

#org @talk2
= Agatha: [.]\c\h08ó\nVery well.\pJust know Samuel won't take kindly\nto your interference.\pIf his old self really has\nreturned[.]\pThere's nothing he wouldn't do to\nkeep enemies like you away.

